	<key>Charge weighs your HRV against your personal baseline (~55%%), resting heart rate (~20%%), rest quality (~15%%), respiration (~5%%) and skin-temperature deviation (~5%%). Effort is a 0–%@ cardiovascular load from time in heart-rate zones. Rest is staged from movement and heart rate. Everything is computed here from the strap's raw data. It works for any day VWAR Loop Life collected raw streams.</key>
