	<key>When you import an Apple Health or WHOOP export, iOS hands VWAR Loop Life a private copy of the file. VWAR Loop Life reads it, saves your data into the health database, then deletes the copy. Older builds didn't delete every copy. This screen reclaims any that were left behind.</key>
